</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Validate</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="54">Validate</strong> to validate the transaction details.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Select <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Post</strong> &gt; <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="55">Post</strong> to post the journal. Fixed asset and ledger transactions are created.</p>
