<li sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77"><p sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">In the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/rus-depreciation-calculation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">Transaction date</strong> field, select the date of the transaction.</p>
